HEADWORD: Space age
<hw>Space age</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>the time during which humans
engaged in space exploration; -- generally considered as beginning on
October 4, 1957 when the Soviet Union placed the first artificial
satellite into orbit around the earth.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

